          &lt;a referrer=&quot;null&quot; href=&quot;https://www.zaobao.com/news/world/story20250421-6222267&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; class=&quot;title&quot; id=&quot;mobile-recommend-articles&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;my-0 line-clamp-4 leading-normal&quot;&gt;
              “人民教宗”方济各逝世：一生倡导宽容 关怀弱势
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;relative min-w-[120px] w-[120px]&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img alt=&quot;“人民教宗”方济各逝世：一生倡导宽容 关怀弱势&quot; title=&quot;“人民教宗”方济各逝世：一生倡导宽容 关怀弱势&quot; src=&quot;https://cassette.sphdigital.com.sg/image/zaobao/75d8588cb06bd71570b4002aad762d72c31878cca0a8f32a9d5994f1a8866d4b&quot; class=&quot;my-0 w-full rounded-[4px] object-contain&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;
